title: Tues Post Show (10-04-22)
itunes:title: Tues Post Show (10-04-22)
description:
We talked about Loretta Lynn passing away at the age of 90. We run through the Top 3 Songs in country music. Bobby gets more into the story about the man who was robbed at gunpoint after setting up a Tinder date. Police in California are trying to find a serial killer. Bobby shows off his new ‘ladies’ watch. We also run through the Top 5 Breakup songs. Bobby also addresses two things listeners are hitting him up about: him saying the “F word” and eating sugar over the weekend. Bobby also gets a special delivery and opens it. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
